channel.title: Wild Things - Zeph [Chill/Future Bass, Mellow]
channel.description: Hello again! Here I am with another track, I will admit, this one was a little easier than other genres I have made. This is a new genre for me though so I don't expect it to top the charts you know? Anyway, I finalized it in a record 2 days lol, that's a first for me since it usually takes me around a week or two to finish a track. Hopefully you enjoy it! Don't hesitate to repost it if you liked it :) [Zeph - Wild Things](https://soundcloud.com/zephprod/wild-things)
